{
  "stem": "5758.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then another one came to tattoo our number on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The number that I have is 157103.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were given a-- we were told to go and be deloused.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were rushed out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was already-- in October, it was already cold in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was really bitterly cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was raining.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had to undress completely in one barrack and run out-- leave our clothes where they are, with shoes and everything, run out completely naked to another barrack, where there were showers and-- and where they sprayed us with-- brushed us with some chemical liquid, delousing us.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had a shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were taken out of that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after the shower, out in the cold again, out in the rain, naked.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went to another block, another barrack, where we were given a pair of trousers, a striped-- all in striped clothes-- jackets, pajamas, and a shirt, and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] some wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were-- the-- the sole was-- was not leather, but it was-- the sole was completely wooden, and the top was like canvas.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not leather, but it was canvas or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Or plastic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were asked to put it on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We still didn't eat anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We still didn't-- you know, for three days and three nights, we did not eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I forgot to mention, naturally, in our wagon, there were two people who died.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That didn't-- they were carried out because they were dead when-- when we arrived in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were terribly hungry, and we were then allocated a barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The barrack-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we saw as we entered the barrack, there was one separate room which was the home of the blockalteste.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
